      Subclasses of TokenClientParam in ca.uhn.fhir.rest.gclient 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  TokenParam
      Deprecated. 
      Use TokenClientParam instead. That class is identical to this one but was renamed to reduct confusing duplicate names in the API. This class will be removed in a future release.
